quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,9,"You who believe, let neither your wealth nor your children distract you from remembering God. Those who do so will be the losers"
  63,10,"Spend something from whatever We have provided you with before death comes to one of you and he says: \"My Lord, if You would only delay things for me for a short while, then I will act charitably and become honorable"
  63,11,God will never postpone things for any soul once its deadline has arrived. God is Informed about anything you do